OL,4,CAfghanistan: Taliban 'tortured and
OL,5,Cmassacred' Hazara minority
OL,6, The Taliban recently "massacred" and
OL,7, brutally tortured several members of
OL,8, the Hazara minority in Afghanistan,
OL,9, says human rights group Amnesty
OL,10, International.
OL,12,FWitnesses have given harrowing accounts
OL,13,Fof the killings, which took place in
OL,14,Fearly July in Ghazni province.
OL,16,FSince taking over the Afghan capital
OL,17,FKabul on Sunday, the Taliban has tried
OL,18,Fto portray a more restrained image.
OL,20,FBut Amnesty said the incident was a
OL,21,F"horrifying indicator" of Taliban rule.
